::Repressor::

Repressor shakes his head. "Lets not give Zardus any more stuff to 
worry about. The programming proccess was probably successful, but we 
should watch her just in case."

He walks over to a console, tapping a few buttons. The room 
dissapeared around them, replaced by a hologram of a large field.

Repressor turns around. "If she does anything suspicious, we can get 
her."

He wields one of his swords. "Do you want to have the first attack?"
